content: I think this list is a great starting point, but I'm wondering if I can get away with packing even fewer clothes. On my last trip to visit my family for Easter, I realized I overpacked and only ended up wearing half of the clothes I brought. I packed 10 shirts, 7 pairs of pants, and 5 dresses, but only wore 3 of the shirts, 4 pairs of pants, and 2 dresses.
